Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大和结婚吗
